    "Then, some widely used machine learning techniques have been used to classify the signals based on the extracted features.",
    "It includes mean, variance, kurtosis, skewness, minimum, maximum, energy, peak frequency, amplitude, and mobility.",
    "Yet, this detection system is required to estimate the detection efficiency of classification with a large amount of data.",
    "Solaija, et al.",
    "18 suggested a new feature selection mechanism named Dynamic Mode Decomposition (DMD) for reducing the dimensionality of features used for EEG signal classification."
